<style>
    /* 1. SECTION AYARLARI */
    #section-hero {
        position: relative !important;
        padding: 130px 0 60px 0 !important;
        min-height: 700px;
    }

    .jarallax-img {
        z-index: -1 !important;
        object-fit: cover !important;
    }

    /* 2. KOMPAKT KART YAPISI */
    .hero-search-form {
        background: white !important;
        border-radius: 12px !important;
        padding: 20px !important;
        box-shadow: 0px 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2) !important;
        max-width: 1050px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
    }

    .form-title {
        color: #1c355e !important;
        font-weight: 700 !important;
        font-size: 13px !important;
        margin-bottom: 8px !important;
        display: block;
    }

    /* 3. KARE YEŞİL KUTULAR */
    .v-selection-group {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .v-type {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
    }

        .v-type input {
            display: none;
        }

        .v-type label {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #26d120 !important; /* İstediğin parlak yeşil */
            color: white;
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 10px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin: 0;
        }

            .v-type label img {
                width: 45px;
                height: auto;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
                filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
            }

            .v-type label span {
                font-weight: 700;
                font-size: 12px;
            }

        .v-type input:checked + label {
            background-color: #1a9e16 !important;
            transform: scale(0.98);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

    /* 4. INPUT VE BUTONLAR */
    .custom-input {
        border: 1px solid #ced4da !important;
        height: 38px !important;
        font-size: 13px !important;
        border-radius: 5px !important;
    }

    .input-group-custom {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .date-field {
        flex: 2;
        border-top-right-radius: 0 !important;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 0 !important;
    }

    .time-field {
        flex: 1;
        border-left: none !important;
        border-top-left-radius: 0 !important;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 0 !important;
    }

    .btn-search {
        background: #26d120 !important;
        color: white !important;
        border: none;
        padding: 8px 25px;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* 5. ADIMLAR ALANI (Geri Getirilen Kısım) */
    .steps-container {
        margin-top: 60px;
        color: white;
    }

    .step-box {
        position: relative;
        padding-right: 15px;
    }

    .step-num {
        background: #26d120;
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: 800;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .step-box h4 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .step-box p {
        font-size: 13px;
        opacity: 0.8;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
</style>

<section id="section-hero" class="jarallax">
    <img src="/rentaly/images/background/1.jpg" class="jarallax-img" alt="">

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center text-light mb-4">
                <h2 style="font-weight: 800;">Looking for a <span class="id-color">vehicle</span>?</h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-search-form">
            <form method="post">
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-lg-5">
                        <span class="form-title">What is your vehicle type?</span>
                        <div class="v-selection-group">
                            <div class="v-type">
                                <input id="car" name="vtype" type="radio" checked><label for="car">
                                    <img src="/rentaly/images/select-form/car.png"><span>Car</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="v-type">
                                <input id="van" name="vtype" type="radio"><label for="van">
                                    <img src="/rentaly/images/select-form/van.png"><span>Van</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="v-type">
                                <input id="mini" name="vtype" type="radio"><label for="mini">
                                    <img src="/rentaly/images/select-form/minibus.png"><span>Minibus</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="v-type">
                                <input id="pres" name="vtype" type="radio"><label for="pres">
                                    <img src="/rentaly/images/select-form/sportscar.png"><span>Prestige</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-7">
                        <div class="row g-2">
                            <div class="col-6">
                                <span class="form-title">Pick Up Location</span>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="Location" class="form-control custom-input">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-6">
                                <span class="form-title">Drop Off Location</span>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="Location" class="form-control custom-input">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-6">
                                <span class="form-title">Pick Up Date & Time</span>
                                <div class="input-group-custom">
                                    <input type="date" class="form-control custom-input date-field">
                                    <select class="form-select custom-input time-field"><option>09:00</option></select>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-6">
                                <span class="form-title">Return Date & Time</span>
                                <div class="input-group-custom">
                                    <input type="date" class="form-control custom-input date-field">
                                    <select class="form-select custom-input time-field"><option>09:00</option></select>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-12 text-end mt-3">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-search">Find a Vehicle</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="step-box">
                        <div class="step-num">1</div>
                        <h4>Bir araç seçin</h4>
                        <p>Her ihtiyaca, zevke ve varış noktasına uygun olarak tasarlanmış geniş araç filomuzla benzersiz maceraların ve unutulmaz yolculukların kilidini açın..</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="step-box">
                        <div class="step-num">2</div>
                        <h4>Konum ve tarih seçin</h4>
                        <p>İdeal konumunuzu ve tarihinizi seçin, biz de sizi rahatlık, esneklik ve unutulmaz deneyimlerle dolu bir yolculuğa çıkaralım..</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="step-box">
                        <div class="step-num">3</div>
                        <h4>Rezervasyon yapın</h4>
                        <p>Rezervasyonunuzu kolaylıkla güvence altına alın, olasılıklar dünyasının kapılarını açın ve bir sonraki maceranıza güvenle başlayın..</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="step-box">
                        <div class="step-num">4</div>
                        <h4>Arkanıza yaslanın ve rahatlayın</h4>
                        <p>Her ayrıntıyla biz ilgilendiğimiz için, zahmetsiz bir kolaylık sunuyoruz; böylece siz rahatlayabilir ve konfor dolu bir yolculuğun tadını çıkarabilirsiniz.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>